        <!-- Q5 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设  <m> X \sim U(0,3), Y \sim P(2), \operatorname{Cov}(X, Y)=-1 </m> , 则  <m> D(2 X-Y+1)=(\quad) </m> 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <choices>
                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            10
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
                
                <choice correct="yes">
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            9
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                           1
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            0
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
            
            </choices>
            
			<answer>
                	<p>
                        <me> 
                            \begin{array}{l}
                            D(2 X-Y+1)\\=D(2 X-Y)\\=D(2 X)+D(Y)-2 \operatorname{COV}(2 X, Y) \\
                            =4 D(X)+D(Y)-4 \operatorname{COV}(X, Y) \\
                            \end{array}
                             </me>  </p> 
                            
                             <p>  <me> X \sim U(a, b) \Rightarrow D(X)=\frac{(b-a)^{2}}{12} ; Y \sim P(\lambda) \Rightarrow D(Y)=\lambda </me>  </p> 
                            
                             <p>  <me> D(2 X-Y+1)=4 \times \frac{(3)^{2}}{12}+2-4(-1)=9 </me>
                	</p>
          	</answer>
		</exercise>


        <!-- Q6 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    已知离散型随机向量  <m> (X, Y) </m>  的概率分布如表,求  <m> \operatorname{cov}(X, Y) </m> . 
                    <me> 
                        \begin{array}{c|ccc}
                        \hline 
                         X\backslash Y   &amp;  -1  &amp;  0  &amp;  2 \\
                        \hline 0  &amp;  0.1  &amp;  0.2  &amp;  0 \\
                        1  &amp;  0.3  &amp;  0.05  &amp;  0.1 \\
                        2  &amp;  0.15  &amp;  0  &amp;  0.1 \\
                        \hline
                        \end{array}
                         </me> 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 容易求得  <m> X </m>  的概率分布为  <m> P\{X=0\}=0.3 </m> ,  <m> P\{X=1\}=0.45, P\{X=2\}=0.25 ; </m> 
                <m>  Y  </m>  的概率分布为
                <me> 
                P\{Y=-1\}=0.55, \quad P\{Y=0\}=0.25, P\{Y=2\}=0.2,
                </me>  </p> 

                <p>  <me> 
                \begin{array}{l}
                E(X)=0 \times 0.3+1 \times 0.45+2 \times 0.25=0.95 \\
                E(Y)=(-1) \times 0.55+0 \times 0.25+2 \times 0.2=-0.15
                \end{array}
                </me>  </p> 

                <p> 计算得
                <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                E(X Y)  &amp;  =0 \times(-1) \times 0.1+0 \times 0 \times 0.2+0 \times 2 \times 0 \\
                &amp;  +1 \times(-1) \times 0.3+1 \times 0 \times 0.5+1 \times 2 \times 0.1 \\
                &amp;  +2 \times(-1) \times 0.15+2 \times 0 \times 0+2 \times 2 \times 0.1=0
                \end{aligned}
                </me>  </p> 

                <p> 于是  <m> \operatorname{cov}(X, Y)=E(X Y)-E(X) E(Y)=0.95 \times 0.15=0.1425 </m> . 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q7 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设连续型随机变量  <m>  (X, Y)  </m>  的密度函数为
                <me> 
                f(x, y)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
                8 x y,  &amp;  0 \leq x \leq y \leq 1 \\
                0,  &amp;  \text { 其它 }
                \end{array},\right.
                </me>  </p> 

                <p> 求  <m> \operatorname{cov}(X, Y) </m>  和  <m> D(X+Y) </m> .
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 由  <m>  (X, Y)  </m>  的密度函数可求得其边缘密度函数分别为:
                    <me> 
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    f_{X}(x)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
                    4 x\left(1-x^{2}\right),  &amp;  0 \leq x \leq 1 \\
                    0,  &amp;  \text { 其它 }
                    \end{array},\right. \\
                    f_{Y}(y)=\left\{\begin{array}{cc}
                    4 y^{3},  &amp;  0 \leq y \leq 1 \\
                    0,  &amp;  \text { 其它 }
                    \end{array},\right.
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me> 
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    E(X)=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} x f_{X}(x) d x=\int_{0}^{1} x \cdot 4 x\left(1-x^{2}\right) d x=8 / 15 \\
                    E(Y)=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} y f_{Y}(y) d y=\int_{0}^{1} y \cdot 4 y^{3} d y=4 / 5 \\
                    E(X Y)=\displaystyle\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} \int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} x y f(x, y) d x d y=\int_{0}^{1} d x \int_{x}^{1} x y \cdot 8 x y \cdot d y =4 / 9, \\
                    \operatorname{cov}(X, Y)=E(X Y)-E(X) E(Y)=4 / 225
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 又
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    E\left(X^{2}\right)  &amp;  =\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} x^{2} f_{X}(x) d x=\int_{0}^{1} x^{2} \cdot 4 x\left(1-x^{2}\right) d x =1 / 3, \\
                    E\left(Y^{2}\right)  &amp;  =\int_{-\infty}^{+\infty} y^{2} f_{Y}(y) d y=\int_{0}^{1} y^{2} \cdot 4 y^{3} d y=2 / 3,
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> 所以  <m> D(X)=E\left(X^{2}\right)-[E(X)]^{2}=11 / 225, D(Y)=E\left(Y^{2}\right)-[E(Y)]^{2}=2 / 75, </m> 故
                    <me> 
                    \begin{aligned}
                    D(X+Y)  &amp;  =D(X)+D(Y)+2 \operatorname{cov}(X, Y)  =1 / 9 .
                    \end{aligned}
                    </me> 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q8 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设随机变量  <m> X, Y </m>  的概率分布相同,  <m> X </m>  的概率分布为  <m> P\{X=0\}=\frac{1}{3}, P\{X=1\}=\frac{2}{3} </m> , 且  <m> X </m>  与  <m> Y </m>  的相关系数为  <m> \rho_{X Y}=\frac{1}{2} </m> . </p> 

                    <p> (I) 求  <m> (X, Y) </m>  的概率分布; </p> 

                    <p> (II) 求  <m> P\{X+Y \leqslant 1\} </m> . 
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解: 从结果推  <m>  P\{X=0, Y=0\}  </m>  等  <m> 4 </m>  个联合概率没有结果, 从已知往后推导
                    <me> 
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    \rho_{x y}=\frac{\operatorname{cov}(X, Y)}{\sqrt{D(X)} \sqrt{D(Y)}}=\frac{\operatorname{COV}(X, Y)}{\sqrt{D(X)} \sqrt{D(Y)}}=\frac{E(X Y)-E(X) E(Y)}{\sqrt{D(X)} \sqrt{D(Y)}}=\frac{1}{2} \\
                    D(X)=E\left(X^{2}\right)-E^{2}(X)=\frac{2}{3}-\frac{4}{9}=\frac{2}{9}=D(Y) ; E(X)=E(Y)=\frac{2}{3}
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me> 
                    \begin{array}{l}
                    E(X Y)=\frac{1}{2} \sqrt{D(X)} \sqrt{D(Y)}+E(X) E(Y)=\frac{1}{9}+\frac{4}{9}=\frac{5}{9} . \\
                    E(X Y)=X Y \cdot P\{X=1, Y=1\}=\frac{5}{9}
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p>  <me> 
                    \begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|}
                    \hline X \backslash Y  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  \text{概率} \\
                    \hline 0  &amp;   2 / 9   &amp;   1 / 9   &amp;   1 / 3  \\
                    \hline 1  &amp;   1 / 9   &amp;   5 / 9   &amp;   2 / 3  \\
                    \hline \text{概率}  &amp;   1 / 3   &amp;   2 / 3   &amp;  1 \\
                    \hline
                    \end{array}
                    </me>  </p> 

                    <p> (2)  <m> P\{X+Y \leq 1\}=P\{X=0, Y=0\}+P\{X=0, Y=1\}+P\{X=1, Y=0\}=4 / 9 </m> . 
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>

        <!-- Q9 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设二维随机变量  <m> (X, Y) </m>  的概率分布为
                    <me> 
                    \begin{array}{|c|c|c|c|}
                    \hline X\backslash Y  &amp;  0  &amp;  1  &amp;  2 \\
                    \hline-1  &amp;  0.1  &amp;  0.1  &amp;  b \\
                    \hline 1  &amp;  a  &amp;  0.1  &amp;  0.1 \\
                    \hline
                    \end{array}
                    </me> 
                    若事件  <m> \{\max (X, Y)=2\} </m>  与事件  <m> \{\min (X, Y)=1\} </m>  相互独立, 则  <m> \operatorname{Cov}(X, Y)=(\quad) </m>
                </p>
            </statement>
            <choices>
                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            <m> -0.6 </m> 
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
                
                <choice correct="yes">
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            <m> -0.36 </m>
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            <m> 0 </m> 
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>

                <choice>
                    <statement>
                        <p>
                            <m> 0.48 </m>
                        </p>
                    </statement>
                </choice>
            
            </choices>
            
			<answer>
                	<p>
                        解:  <m> P\{\max (X, Y)=2\}=P\{X=-1, Y=2\}+P\{X=1, Y=2\}=b+0.1 </m> ,
                        <m> P\{\min (X, Y)=1\}=P\{X=1, Y=2\}+P\{X=1, Y=1\}=0.1+0.1 </m> 
                        <m> P\{\min (X, Y)=1, \max (X, Y)=2\}=P\{X=1, Y=2\}=0.1 </m> , 由相互独立的公式得
                        <m> P\{\min (X, Y)=1, \max (X, Y)=2\}=P\{\max (X, Y)=2\} P\{\min (X, Y)=1\} </m> , 有  <m> 0.1=0.2(b+0.1), b=0.4 </m> ,由规范性得  <m> a=0.2 </m> . 
                       协方差为  <m> \operatorname{Cov}(X, Y)=E(X Y)-E(X) E(Y)=-0.36 </m>
                	</p>
          	</answer>
		</exercise>


        <!-- Q10 -->
        <exercise>
            <statement>
                <p>
                    设随机变量  <m> X \sim N(1,9), Y \sim N(0,16) X </m>  与  <m> Y </m>  的相关系数  <m> \rho=-0.5 </m> ,设  <m> Z=\frac{X}{3}+\frac{Y}{2} </m> 
                (1) 求  <m> E(Z), D(Z) </m> ;
                (2) 求  <m> X </m>  与  <m> Z </m>  的相关系数
                </p>
            </statement>
            <answer>
                <p>
                    解:(1)  <m> EZ=\frac{1}{3} EX+\frac{1}{2} E Y=\frac{1}{3} \times 1+\frac{1}{2} \times 0=\frac{1}{3}  </m> 
                <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                D Z  &amp;  =D\left(\frac{1}{3} \mathrm{X}+\frac{1}{2} Y\right)=\frac{1}{9} \mathrm{DX}+\frac{1}{4} D Y+\frac{1}{6} \times 2 \operatorname{cov}(\mathrm{X}, Y) \\
                &amp;  =\frac{1}{9} \mathrm{DX}+\frac{1}{4} D Y+\frac{1}{6} \times 2 \times \rho_{X Y} \sqrt{D X} \sqrt{D Y}=3
                \end{aligned}
                </me>  </p> 

                <p> (2) </p> 

                <p>  <me> 
                \begin{aligned}
                \operatorname{cov}(X, Z) &amp; =\operatorname{cov}\left(X, \frac{1}{3} X+\frac{1}{2} Y\right)\\ &amp; =\operatorname{cov}\left(X, \frac{1}{3} X\right)+\operatorname{cov}\left(X, \frac{1}{2} Y\right) \\
                &amp; =\frac{1}{3} D X+\frac{1}{2} \operatorname{cov}(X, Y)\\ &amp; =\frac{1}{3} \times 9+\frac{1}{2} \rho_{X Y} \sqrt{D X} \sqrt{D Y}\\ &amp; =3+\frac{1}{2} \times \frac{-1}{2} \times 3 \times 4=0
                \end{aligned}
                </me>  </p> 

                <p>  <m> \therefore X, Z </m>  不相关
                </p>
            </answer>
        </exercise>



